Interface OptionContentPresenter.ColorFrameView

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AcrolinxOptionsPreferenceView, OptionContentPresenter.OptionContentView, OptionContentPresenter.PluginTabView, OptionPresenter.OptionView
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcrolinxOptionsPreferencePage, OptionDialog, OptionDialog, PluginOptionComposite, PluginOptionsPanel
    Enclosing class:
    OptionContentPresenter

    public static interface OptionContentPresenter.ColorFrameView
    The OptionContentPresenter.ColorFrameView is the part of OptionContentPresenter.OptionContentView displaying the color settings. It is part of the plug-in-tab.
